INSERT INTO `tb_page_layanan` VALUES (1,'ID-RANK','<p><strong>Webometric</strong> adalah salah satu perangkat atau sistem untuk mengukur atau memberikan penilaian terhadap kemajuan seluruh universitas atau perguruan tinggi terbaik di dunia (World Class University) melalui Website universitas tersebut.</p>','1524485900.jpg','2018-04-23 12:18:20'),(2,'ID-RESEARCH','<p>IDREN mewadahi penelitian menggunakan infrastruktur IDREN. Beberapa alternatif penelitian seperti:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n <li>Software-Defined Networking</li>\r\n <li>IoT</li>\r\n <li>Pengembangan protokol baru</li>\r\n <li>Big Data Analytic</li>\r\n <li>dsb.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>IDREN juga mengembangkan inisiatif berbagi pakai data penelitian, melalui inisiatif Indonesia Open Research Data (IOReD). Selain itu trafik domestik antar member dapat lebih efisien dengan hop yang lebih pendek, dan penyediaan akses langsung ke TEIN/global REN.</p>','1524472276.jpg','2018-04-24 07:05:26'),(3,'ID-BOOK','<p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Donec molestie, est vel posuere tincidunt, ante augue maximus lacus, quis placerat erat mi vestibulum mauris. Proin eu scelerisque urna. Aliquam auctor diam et mi convallis, id varius justo dapibus. Pellentesque orci purus, lacinia non tincidunt et, euismod non ex. Praesent dui enim, vestibulum ut elementum sed, ornare eget lacus. Etiam nibh lorem, finibus vitae quam eu, ultrices tempus libero. Aliquam fermentum convallis tortor ut laoreet.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Quisque commodo metus ligula. Curabitur molestie nulla nec turpis varius rutrum. Donec ac scelerisque dui. Sed ac neque euismod, bibendum augue eu, sodales eros. Donec faucibus quis neque sit amet maximus. Fusce posuere vulputate euismod. Nullam sed mattis orci, nec vestibulum ex.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Duis molestie vestibulum nisi. Pellentesque et libero dolor. Aliquam et aliquet tortor. Sed nec tortor tempor, sodales nisl nec, fringilla magna. Morbi nec metus risus. Etiam nec vulputate nisi, sed rutrum ipsum. Integer mollis vel quam non consequat. Donec eleifend eleifend molestie. Sed vestibulum mattis vestibulum.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ut lobortis vulputate pharetra. Sed vitae lacinia mi. Ut venenatis auctor tellus, ac dignissim sem maximus non. Nullam a molestie mi. Nunc convallis metus sed elit dapibus efficitur. Aliquam at scelerisque augue. Sed elementum mauris ut ex condimentum, pellentesque suscipit tellus eleifend. Sed sit amet ultrices ligula, sed sagittis orci. Nunc semper nec mauris ac tincidunt. Praesent fringilla, neque sagittis semper porta, ex nisi volutpat felis, in commodo mauris mi a odio. Etiam pharetra, ante at commodo dapibus, nibh nulla porttitor lectus, eget sollicitudin odio odio porttitor justo.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Donec ac aliquam est, sit amet condimentum dui. Aliquam malesuada eros nec suscipit tristique. Phasellus eleifend leo bibendum nulla maximus semper. Nunc ornare lectus et nisi egestas, sit amet commodo diam varius. Proin tempus sapien sed lectus tempus, rutrum ultricies leo accumsan. Morbi laoreet sit amet arcu et facilisis. Quisque tellus libero, molestie eu massa quis, accumsan mattis felis. Praesent aliquam nulla vel libero placerat blandit. Morbi varius turpis in mi imperdiet finibus. Aenean ut bibendum sapien, vel fermentum leo. Suspendisse ultrices interdum magna quis euismod. Aliquam ac gravida augue.</p>','1524472575.jpg','2018-04-23 08:36:15'),(4,'ID-JOURNAL','<p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Donec molestie, est vel posuere tincidunt, ante augue maximus lacus, quis placerat erat mi vestibulum mauris. Proin eu scelerisque urna. Aliquam auctor diam et mi convallis, id varius justo dapibus. Pellentesque orci purus, lacinia non tincidunt et, euismod non ex. Praesent dui enim, vestibulum ut elementum sed, ornare eget lacus. Etiam nibh lorem, finibus vitae quam eu, ultrices tempus libero. Aliquam fermentum convallis tortor ut laoreet.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Quisque commodo metus ligula. Curabitur molestie nulla nec turpis varius rutrum. Donec ac scelerisque dui. Sed ac neque euismod, bibendum augue eu, sodales eros. Donec faucibus quis neque sit amet maximus. Fusce posuere vulputate euismod. Nullam sed mattis orci, nec vestibulum ex.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Duis molestie vestibulum nisi. Pellentesque et libero dolor. Aliquam et aliquet tortor. Sed nec tortor tempor, sodales nisl nec, fringilla magna. Morbi nec metus risus. Etiam nec vulputate nisi, sed rutrum ipsum. Integer mollis vel quam non consequat. Donec eleifend eleifend molestie. Sed vestibulum mattis vestibulum.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ut lobortis vulputate pharetra. Sed vitae lacinia mi. Ut venenatis auctor tellus, ac dignissim sem maximus non. Nullam a molestie mi. Nunc convallis metus sed elit dapibus efficitur. Aliquam at scelerisque augue. Sed elementum mauris ut ex condimentum, pellentesque suscipit tellus eleifend. Sed sit amet ultrices ligula, sed sagittis orci. Nunc semper nec mauris ac tincidunt. Praesent fringilla, neque sagittis semper porta, ex nisi volutpat felis, in commodo mauris mi a odio. Etiam pharetra, ante at commodo dapibus, nibh nulla porttitor lectus, eget sollicitudin odio odio porttitor justo.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Donec ac aliquam est, sit amet condimentum dui. Aliquam malesuada eros nec suscipit tristique. Phasellus eleifend leo bibendum nulla maximus semper. Nunc ornare lectus et nisi egestas, sit amet commodo diam varius. Proin tempus sapien sed lectus tempus, rutrum ultricies leo accumsan. Morbi laoreet sit amet arcu et facilisis. Quisque tellus libero, molestie eu massa quis, accumsan mattis felis. Praesent aliquam nulla vel libero placerat blandit. Morbi varius turpis in mi imperdiet finibus. Aenean ut bibendum sapien, vel fermentum leo. Suspendisse ultrices interdum magna quis euismod. Aliquam ac gravida augue.</p>','1524473595.png','2018-04-23 08:53:15'),(5,'ID-TUBE','<p>Portal video berupa tutorial, materi pengajaran, materi kuliah jarak jauh, dll.</p>','1524486115.jpg','2018-04-23 12:21:55'),(6,'ID-MAIL','<p>Member IDREN mendapatkan akun  <a href=\"http://mail.idren.id/#/login\">Email IDREN</a>  sebagai media kolaborasi. Jika anda belum memiliki akun @idren.id, silahkan hubungi hello@idren.id untuk info lebih lanjut dan dapatkan akun email gratis 30GB !</p>','1524477706.jpg','2018-04-24 00:15:07'),(7,'ID-LINKS','<p>Introduction</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>eduroam</strong> (education roaming) is an international roaming service for users in research, higher education and further education. It provides researchers, teachers and students easy and secure network access when visiting an institution other than their own. Authentication of users is performed by their home institution, using the same credentials as when they access the network locally, while authorization to access the Internet and possibly other resources is handled by the visited institution. Users do not have to pay for using eduroam.</p>\r\n\r\n<p> </p>\r\n\r\n<p>How does eduroam work?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>eduroam is built with IEEE 802.1X (a standard for port based Network Access Control) and <strong>RADIUS</strong> (Remote Authentication Dial-In User Service).eduroam is a federated authentication service that allows participating institutions to provide access to their wireless networks to users from other eduroam participating institutions using the institutional username/password credentials they use at their home institution for wireless network access. eduroam is based on a federated authentication model where your username and password are validated by your home institution (your identity provider) and access to authorised network services is controlled by the institution you are visiting (the service provider).</p>\r\n\r\n<p> </p>\r\n\r\n<p>For more information please click <a href=\"https://eduroamid.info/\" target=\"_blank\">here</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p> </p>','1524545468.png','2018-04-24 08:41:35'),(10,'MONITORING GRAPH','<p>IDREN (AS64302) memiliki MRTG untuk memantau koneksi setiap node secara periodik.  MRTG (the Multi Router Traffic Grapher) adalah aplikasi yang digunakan untuk memantau beban trafik pada <em>link</em> jaringan. MRTG akan membuat halaman HTML yang berisi gambar GIF yang mengambarkan trafik melalui jaringan secara harian, mingguan, bulanan dan tahunan.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Tools lain selain MRTG adalah Smokeping. Smokeping adalah tools yang biasa digunakan oleh Network Administrator untuk mengetahui kualitas jaringan, beberapa parameter yang ditampilkan oleh smokeping adalah latency dan packet loss.</p>\r\n\r\n<p> </p>\r\n\r\n<p>Untuk memonitor trafik node IDREN, silahkan <strong>login</strong> terlebih dahulu.</p>','1524480428.jpg','2018-04-23 12:01:30');
